OL,3,CPolice investigate 'racially motivated
OL,4,Chate crime' in west Belfast
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a "racially
OL,7,Fmotivated hate crime" in west Belfast.
OL,9,FDetectives are appealing for witnesses
OL,10,Fto the incident in the Divis Street
OL,11,Farea reported shortly after 1.20pm on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FIt was reported that a man was
OL,15,Ffollowed by a male with a dog who
OL,16,Fsubjected him to racial verbal abuse.
