OL,6,F"He proceeded to follow him to his
OL,7,Fhome address and continued to be
OL,8,Fverbally abusive and made threats
OL,9,Ftowards him," Detective Sergeant
OL,10,FMcCartan said.
OL,12,F"The suspect then tried to gain entry
OL,13,Fto the property whilst assaulting the
OL,14,Fmale occupant, and striking him with a
OL,15,Fmetal dog lead.
OL,17,F"He continued to try and enter the
OL,18,Fproperty to assault the occupant but
OL,19,Feventually fled after a number of
OL,20,Fother residents intervened.
