OL,6,F"The victim subsequently attended
OL,7,Fhospital for treatment for injuries to
OL,8,Fhis arm."
OL,10,FThe detective sergeant said the
OL,11,F"prolonged assault" was being
OL,12,Finvestigated as a racially motivated
OL,13,Fhate crime.
OL,15,F"An investigation is under way, and we
OL,16,Fwould appeal to anyone who may have
OL,17,Fseen what happened, or who has any
OL,18,Finformation which could assist us, to
OL,19,Fcontact 101, and quote reference
OL,20,Fnumber 839 of 27/03/25."
